        "text": "Event is about to start - final reminder sent!\n\nEVENT: {{ $json.event_name }}\nVENUE: {{ $json.venue_name }}\nSTART TIME: {{ $json.event_date }} at {{ $json.event_time }}\n\nFACEBOOK PERFORMANCE:\n- Total RSVPs: {{ $json.rsvp_count }}\n- Attending: {{ $json.attending_count }}\n- Interested: {{ $json.interested_count }}\n\nPROMOTION SUMMARY:\n- Reminders Sent: {{ $json.reminders_sent }}\n- Event URL: {{ $json.facebook_event_url }}\n- Ticket Link: {{ $json.ticket_link }}\n\nNext: Post-event follow-up in 24 hours.",
